summary: This is a retexture package for Skyrim. Gives higher resolution textures. WARNING DO NOT USE IF YOU HAVE A SUCKY OR CRAPPY PC
descriptionHtml:
This is a retexture package for Skyrim. Gives higher resolution textures. WARNING DO NOT USE IF YOU HAVE A SUCKY OR CRAPPY PC --- Meaning anything less than these requirements will make you Lag.


Requirements:

Windows 7/Vista PC (64 bit)
Quad-core Intel or AMD CPU processor
8GB System RAM
15GB free HDD (Hard disk drive) space
DirectX 9.0c compatible NVIDIA or AMD ATI video card with 1.5GB of RAM: Nvidia GeForce GTX 260 or higher; ATI Radeon HD 4890 or higher
DirectX compatible sound card
Fast Internet
author: Sammyvan
